Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,360)}喜歡貓的牙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,360)}花花公子佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,360)}繪畫很差勁的佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,365)}沒有精神的凱老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,260)}鬥志高昂的卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,360)}和以往不太一樣的同伴們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,360)}已經過世的父親和母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7.28 震撼高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週六即將公映的《火影忍者》劇場版
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《火影忍者》大電影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本已經陣亡的曉突然出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然齊心協力擊退了敵人 但未能緝拿他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次 面具男子出現在鳴人和小櫻的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎一樣的瞳術將鳴人和小櫻捲入另一個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡遇見了和以往不太一樣的同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想做貓的使者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠都伴隨在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等美麗的風景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春一去不復返
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說嘛 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人和小櫻與一群性格完全相反的同伴們同行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人竟然碰到了已經過世的皆人和櫛名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:00:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.00,0:01:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽的外號可是血色小辣椒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這充滿謎團的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人不斷挑戰面具男的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡有重要的消息發佈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去電影院觀影就附贈豪華特典
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先入場的150萬名觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可領取特別版DVD以及眾人對戰卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來今天的專題就介紹特別版DVD的影像內容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人矚目的內容是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作者岸本老師繪製特典DVD外殼的全過程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有更為珍貴的訪談影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本齊史長篇採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡電影的岸本老師幹勁從何而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常就很喜歡看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過很多電影後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會有類似「如果是我會怎麼做」的遐想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這次親自參與其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說能隨心所欲地發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是打算乾脆按自己喜歡的套路來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後決不可錯過的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作漫畫的各個有名篇幅將會重現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強大震撼的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面請關注特別版DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能得到你的九尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在謎一樣的世界裡遭遇到各種考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越父母是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終鳴人的命運將是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴 家人 羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會守護到底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者之路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影忍者大電影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週六終於要公映了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必去電影院觀影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,好不容易休假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,竟然差遣我出來做苦力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 閃電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 是小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 我這就去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從外表看 傷不重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨骼正常 內臟完好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到跌落的高度…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這徒弟的身體異常強壯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體還好 看來腦部有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是失憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該是暫時的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然見過很多病患
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個病例很罕見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞可能一輩子都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 才16歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的人生還很漫長…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去查查資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就靜觀其變…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是天生的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不自然啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是最近才豐滿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…上天的恩賜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人 頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以打頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有經過這種刺激 醫治好的病例呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻現在比較特別…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬容點啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說小櫻 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧乳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是標準尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音前輩 要寬容一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知天高地厚也該有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我陪你一起趟渾水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 真的什麼都不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少有些印象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少知道這裡是我曾經住過的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外的感覺就很模糊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會送你回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨他們居然不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能置這樣的小櫻於不顧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說井野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真的是我家嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的啊 從出生起到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直守護著你長大的家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從出生起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 乾脆將那傢伙也拖下水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡怎麼也沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明朋友有難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你同班戰友的家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是一個班的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還指望他能讓你想到些什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是什麼樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金黃色的頭髮 一臉呆相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿橘紅色的衣服 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很健忘 很白癡 神經大條
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超喜歡吃拉麵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起什麼來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那個人的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉燒 海帶 玉米…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼偏偏猜不中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鳴人（鳴門卷）啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為能想起什麼來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來成功可沒那麼容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個和你相處較長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是佐助吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在因為某些原因不在村裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但平時總是很冷酷 黑髮的帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才突然強烈地浮現出那樣的感覺 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提到佐助不過這樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當嚴重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 我一定會治好你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看見失憶的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計第一個忘掉的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我們那些酸甜苦澀的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然全被抹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有過那樣的日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙有點不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底怎樣才能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人說是去查查看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞可能一直這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候 身為朋友的我們更應當出手相助了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 什麼都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得哪些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會盡全力協助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對大家有些印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但關鍵的地方感覺有些不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕現在相當混亂的緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 真可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就迎合小櫻的記憶試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…雖然贊成…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這木葉的愛犬派…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然淪落到貓派門下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到精神會如此受刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作些 志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是為了小櫻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛田大小姐 委屈您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我倆要和大家離這麼遠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還被綁得嚴嚴實實的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們 特別是寧次在小櫻身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就會感到毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做錯什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不住了 寧次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是請求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲劇啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個是什麼樣的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的有助於她恢復記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺大家都變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這樣如果能喚回記憶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就相當值了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實奉陪到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁次 戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有鹿丸 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來能否變得呆一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 保持微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得差一點那模糊的印象就能變清晰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經盡力了 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總覺得很不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會突然出現在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且村子的事也好 大家的事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然都有些模糊的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個家我卻完全沒印象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像第一次來到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 叔叔 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是橋那邊的商店街的特賣日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就買過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些就是戰利品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然又重 也很遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但千里之行始於足下嘛 開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 現在有件更重要的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 難道發生戰鬥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去泡個澡忘掉一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 井野都要反感了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母還是這麼厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然父母都回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一見到他們兩人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我的冷笑話感動她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼好好就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是胸口刺痛著 苦悶著…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總不能這麼下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我一直陪著你 等你冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的掛墜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛墜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你今天的確帶著沒見過的掛飾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 我從來沒摘下過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能弄丟的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要我全力跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 你是不是在找東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了丟三落四的年紀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒吐槽你老爸 真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西好像相當重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄丟的是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛掉在家門口了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我大吃一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的完全一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三防線…已經
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會買一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是父女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後可要小心 別再弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 我們可是特意追過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不表示一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…叔叔 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在小櫻她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至於痛哭流涕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻神經錯亂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓…我特別開心呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太喜歡你們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕在吃飯之前回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺一頭霧水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 想起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會從那裡摔下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受火影之命 前往執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就在這附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道被強大的力量牽引
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我察覺後 就已經在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或許並非你所熟知的小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非這個世界的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然記憶沒恢復啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會一直陪伴你左右的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會努力閱讀醫術 好好學習
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡我們也是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但什麼術式都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或許並非你所熟知的小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我認識的小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,本月的獎品是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,在明信片上寫下必須事項和尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,寄往上述地址
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,將抽取40名幸運觀眾贈送獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,為何依附於忍者 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,你這樣還算是武士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我並非依附於忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,讓我殫精竭慮死忠的只有和平
